name: Timedox
description:
You traveled back in time and forgot about time paradoxes, overcome and traverse through tough and challenging levels. Versions of you from the time you traveled from will appear as well, copying your exact path which you will need to avoid.

Made in three days for no reason.

The music is reused from the music in our GMTK 2020 Game Jam submission, which you can find here: https://nulledwine.itch.io/insanity

Benjamin Wang: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl3QNya9p-BJlk3zQO2mAyA

Controls

Move with WASD or your arrow keys

Jump with Z
